/**
 * Enhanced Error Classification System
 *
 * Comprehensive error classification, analysis, and recovery system for umuo.app.
 * This module provides intelligent error handling with pattern recognition,
 * clustering, prediction, and automated recovery strategies, including:
 * - Network interruption handling with automatic retry (T062)
 * - Intelligent error classification (T057)
 * - Automated recovery strategies (T058)
 */

